FruitBang KEYBINDINGS
═════════════════════

NOTE: Super = Windows Key


APPLICATIONS
───────────────────────

Super + Return          Terminal (foot)
Super + Space           Launcher (rofi)
Super + w               Web Browser (firefox)
Super + p               Screenshot


WINDOW CONTROLS
───────────────────────

Super + q               Close Window
Super + s               Toggle Float
Super + f               Fullscreen
Super + Shift + f       Fake Fullscreen
Super + a               Maximise
Super + i               Minimise
Super + Shift + I       Restore Minimised
Super + z               Scratchpad
Super + o               Toggle Overlay


FOCUS & MOVEMENT
───────────────────────

Super + Tab             Next Window
Super + Shift + ←/→/↑/↓  Swap Window Direction
Ctrl + Shift + ←/→/↑/↓   Move Window (50px)
Ctrl + Super + ←/→/↑/↓   Resize Window (50px)


WORKSPACES
───────────────────────

Super + [1-9]           Switch to Workspace
Super + Left/Right      Previous/Next Workspace
Ctrl + Left/Right       Previous/Next (with window)

Super + Shift + [1-9]   Send Window to Workspace (stay here)
Super + Ctrl  + [1-9]   Send Window to Workspace (follow it)


LAYOUT
───────────────────────

Super + n               Switch Layout Mode
Super + e               Set Proportion Full
Super + x               Cycle Proportion Preset
Super + g               Toggle Gaps
Super + Shift + X       Increase Gaps
Super + Shift + Z       Decrease Gaps


MULTI-MONITOR
───────────────────────

Super + Alt + Left/Right        Focus Monitor
Super + Ctrl + Alt + Left/Right Send to Monitor


SYSTEM
───────────────────────

Super + l               Lock Screen
Super + r               Reload Config
Super + m               Quit MangoWM
Vol Up (XF86)           Increase Volume
Vol Down (XF86)         Decrease Volume
Mute (XF86)             Toggle Mute
